name: Water on Mars
description:
The discovery of water on Mars could provide proof that there was once life on our neighboring planet. The face on Mars sheds a tear for all extinct extraterrestrials. 

Part of the series "Dr. Howard’s Voyage to the Astral Realm with ETs and the Face on Mars," a series of nine GIFs following the tale of paranormal researcher Dr. Howard, Mars, and the astral plane.
